1.0.name: wordpress/r2d2
1.0.description: R2D2 is a child theme of the beautiful Twenty Thirteen. The Twenty Thirteen brings WordPress default theme back to blogging. While I adore the typography and it's responsive design I needed something darker and to keep the post titles above the content.
